  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0b89\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b85\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcb\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b9a\u0bc0\u0ba9\u0bbe",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "We are closely monitoring the situation in Sri Lanka - China",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Chinese Foreign Ministry Spokesperson Wang Wenbin said that he is closely monitoring the current situation in Sri Lanka, and expressed his hope that they can work together to restore stability in Sri Lanka and restore the badly affected economy.",
        "Wang Wenbin said the above while participating in a press conference organized on Monday the 11th to answer the questions raised by journalists on various issues globally.",
        "In this meeting, the President was on the verge of stepping down as a result of months of protests by the Sri Lankan people, and therefore China's position on the current situation in Sri Lanka was questioned by a journalist.",
        "Responding to that, Chinese Foreign Ministry Spokesperson Wang Wenbin said that China is closely observing the current situation in Sri Lanka.",
        "At the same time, he also pointed out that as Sri Lanka's neighboring friendly country and as a cooperation partner, all sectors of the country will be improved to meet the basic expectations of the country and its people.",
        "It is noteworthy that Wang Wenbin expressed his hope that we can work together to resolve the current crisis, restore stability in the country, restore the severely affected economy, and improve people's livelihood as quickly as possible."
      ],
